Name: Region
Description: Geographic region from which the session has been started by the visitor

Name: TrafficType
Description: Traffic source by which the visitor has arrived at the Web site (e.g., banner, SMS, direct)

Name: VisitorType
Description: Visitor type as New Visitor, Returning Visitor, and Other

Name: Weekend
Description: Boolean value indicating whether the date of the visit is weekend

Name: Month
Description: Month value of the visit date

Name: Revenue
Description: Class label indicating whether the visit has been finalized with a transaction
